lead_paragraph: Salomon Rondon struck a dramatic equaliser two minutes into stoppage time to earn West Bromwich Albion a crucial point against Swansea City at the Hawthorns.

headline.print_headline: Rondon Earns Last-Gasp Relief for West Brom
